sequenceDiagram
  %% 現状の1回の memory query シーケンス図: 1回の質問が回答か停止理由になるまでを見る

  actor User as 人 / Codex
  participant RX as research_x
  participant Policy as SearchLens / ObjectiveRoutePolicy
  participant Routes as Route Portfolio
  participant Guard as ProviderApiBudgetGuard
  participant Evidence as Source Bundle / Context / Citation
  participant Authority as AnswerAuthorityGatekeeper
  participant Boundary as Answer Boundary
  participant Trace as 実行記録

  User->>RX: 質問と目的を渡す
  RX->>Trace: sidecar trace を開始する
  RX->>Policy: 関心・目的・制約を整理する
  Policy->>Routes: 候補ルートを選ぶ

  opt provider-backed ルートが必要
    Routes->>Guard: 実行可否を確認する
    Guard-->>Trace: provider_gated または実行可を記録する
  end

  Routes-->>RX: candidates
  RX->>Evidence: source bundle / context chunk / citation を確認する
  Evidence->>Authority: claim support を見る
  Authority->>Boundary: answer support または停止理由
  Boundary-->>RX: answer / needs_review / source_not_restored / citation_missing / hypothesis_only / provider_gated
  RX->>Trace: route / guard / evidence / stop reason を残す
  RX-->>User: citations と status を返す
